-- ⊨ :  Entailment

infix 1 _⊨_ _⊨'_
_⊨_ _⊨'_ :  Propᵒ →  Propᵒ →  Set₂
Pᵒ ⊨ Qᵒ =  ∀ {a} →  ✓ a →  Pᵒ .!ᵒ a →  Qᵒ .!ᵒ a
Pᵒ ⊨' Qᵒ =  ∀ {a} →  Pᵒ .!ᵒ a →  Qᵒ .!ᵒ a

